  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Unique and Brand-New Elimination Method</strong><br>Connect 3 or more identical security systems to eliminate them and gain penetration rate.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Features:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >6 different types of security systems, with the largest being the challenging \"361\" system.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dynamic levels randomly generated for each playthrough—no repetitive experiences.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Freely connect systems not just up, down, left, and right, but also diagonally.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Satisfying and relaxing gameplay.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Chill background music.</p></li></ul>",
